      "acceptanceCriteria": "Order-of-accuracy verification using manufactured solutions for both Navier-Stokes and hemolysis transport equations; convergence rates documented.",
      "rationale": "Order-of-accuracy tests were performed for the flow solver but not for the hemolysis power-law transport equation. Convergence rate documentation is partial. Achieved level 2 against required level 4."
