      "achievedLevel": 3,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Experimental boundary conditions replicated in simulation within measurement uncertainty; fluid temperature, hematocrit, and inlet velocity profiles matched.",
      "rationale": "Flow rate and rotational speed boundary conditions are well matched to bench test; hematocrit variability across experiments was documented but not propagated into the simulation boundary conditions. Achieved level 3 against required level 4."
