      "factorType": "Output comparison",
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "requiredLevel": 4,
      "achievedLevel": 2,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Quantitative comparison metric (e.g., E% or U95 band) applied to hemolysis index across all 5 operating points; systematic and random experimental error accounted for.",
      "rationale": "Comparisons are presented graphically with percent error at each operating point; experimental measurement uncertainty is not formally propagated into the comparison metric. Achieved level 2 against required level 4."
