      "acceptanceCriteria": "Sensitivity analysis comparing at least two turbulence models and two hemolysis power-law formulations; model form uncertainty quantified and included in total uncertainty budget.",
      "rationale": "Only the SST k-omega turbulence model and a single hemolysis power-law were used. No model form sensitivity study was conducted. This is a critical epistemic gap at MRL 5 and the factor remains not-assessed."
    },
