    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "The 13-factor credibility assessment has been completed under the Minimal profile. All required fields are populated and a sha256 content hash has been recorded to support future integrity verification. The digital signature workflow is pending organisational PKI provisioning; the signature field will be appended upon workflow completion. On the basis of the available evidence and the Monte Carlo uncertainty quantification, the assessment team accepts the package for submission subject to the outstanding signature step. Six factors remain not-assessed, representing epistemic gaps that are acknowledged and will be addressed in a subsequent COU revision.",
